{
  "stem": "9728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he shook hands with some of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't shake hands with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I saw him very close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As close as-- a couple--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that he was a high-- a high general.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't know that he was the Chief of the American Staff or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time we were feeling-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And let me point out that the Germans also brought in some German-- German doctors into Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, [BACKGROUND NOISE] one doctor that-- examined me, he was in a uniform; in a uniform, but in a very humane way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either he probably was not an SS man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He probably was from the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Feldafing itself behind our camp there is a little village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of them, that they were real sick, they were already transported to that-- to the village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over there they were German doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, as I said, I was examined in camp by a German doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he prescribed some lamp, some heating lamps, some massages, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they did not have any dentists there at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was in that camp, oh, for quite a while, probably.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Til that-- til November.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In November, I decided that I will go back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went-- While I was in Feldafing, we went on several times to Munich to the committee to find out who was alive, and where was alive, and if they have any list.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, in the Jewish committee, you know we put up our lists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am so and so from so and so, and I survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
